title: Ivan Kalchuk
text:
Ivan Sergeyevich Kalchuk (; born 8 May 1991) is a former <a href="Russia">Russia</a>n professional <a href="Association%20football">football</a> player.
Club career.
He made his <a href="Russian%20Football%20National%20League">Russian Football National League</a> debut for <a href="FC%20SKA-Energiya%20Khabarovsk">FC SKA-Energiya Khabarovsk</a> on 15 May 2012 in a game against <a href="FC%20Torpedo%20Vladimir">FC Torpedo Vladimir</a>.
